flowchart LR
    User[User] --> UI[WinUI 3 desktop app]
    User --> CLI[CLYR CLI]
    UI --> AppService[Application services]
    CLI --> AppService
    AppService --> Scanner[Scan engine]
    AppService --> Classifier[Classifier and insight engine]
    AppService --> Snapshots[Snapshot and diff engine]
    AppService -. Phase 5+ .-> Planner[Cleanup plan engine]
    Scanner --> WinAdapter[Windows adapters]
    Classifier --> RuleEngine[Versioned rule engine]
    Planner --> RuleEngine
    Snapshots --> DB[(SQLite)]
    RuleEngine --> Rules[(Built-in and reviewed rule packs)]
    Planner -. Phase 6+ .-> NormalActions[Non-elevated action executor]
    Planner -. Phase 6+ .-> ElevationClient[Elevation client]
    ElevationClient -. typed authenticated request .-> Helper[Short-lived elevated helper]
    NormalActions -. allowlisted action .-> Windows[Windows APIs and supported tool adapters]
    Helper -. allowlisted action .-> Windows
    AppService -. Phase 6+ .-> Audit[Action journal and receipts]
    Audit --> DB
